{"tid":1969234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中泰大戰開打  稱「台灣女孩風」小粉紅玻璃碎光","createTime":"2020-04-12T09:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T13:09:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19e940bead930b1f5a91eabed7e2ace82e2d7438","tid":1969234,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"泰國BL劇《假偶天成》男主角之一Bright和女友nnevvy私下對話被翻出，一句「台灣女孩風格」，意外引發中泰網友大戰，泰國網友製作多張梗圖嘲諷中國，「Taiwan」成為焦點，不少泰國網友高呼「台灣是主權獨立國家」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2020/04/12/3131307_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F3131307_1.jpg&h=dc22fac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBright演出泰國BL劇《假偶天成》。（翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\nBright曾在女友美照下留言：「真好看，像中國女孩！」nnevvy則回應：「what？？」後續有人問是什麼風格時，nnevvy表示：「台灣女孩風喔！」這句話打碎了中國網友的玻璃心，認為她有意分化台灣和中國。再加上nnevvy轉發武漢肺炎貼文時Bright按讚，完全引爆中國網友怒火。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2020/04/12/3131307_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F3131307_2.jpg&h=52adfd20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nnnevvy（右）自稱走「台灣女孩風」，不是「中國女孩」，引發中國網友不爽。（翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤大戰中，中國盜版的《假偶天成》字幕組揚言不會再翻譯《假偶天成》，泰國網友則卯起來酸：「台灣就是台灣」、「武漢肺炎來自中國」、「台灣是國家，香港是國家」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/3131307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3131307&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zojy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=90feda52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3131307&h=bc33547e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/3131307</a>"},{"pid":"6905992137e527640eec61e0133f36ef5b124efa","tid":1969234,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:09:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係時候改變習慣<br />\n講兩個國家嘅時候，如果有蚑那，請將蚑那擺到最後面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1945303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1945303</a></span></span>"}]}